item.title: CVE-2020-4766|2024-08-04T08:14:58.113Z -- ibm -- mq%20internet%20pass-thru
item.description: IBM MQ Internet Pass-Thru 2.1 and 9.2 could allow a remote user to cause a denial of service by sending malformed MQ data requests which would consume all available resources. IBM X-Force ID: 188093.
